Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.84,0:01:44.40,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAubrey\fs50\c&HFFFFFF&\frz1.12\be1\blur4\3a&H64&\bord2\3c&HA2C26B&\fad(0,200)}If we mess up, let's pretend it's a rehearsal and redo it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:55.21,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAubrey\fs50\c&HFFFFFF&\frz1.12\be1\blur4\3a&H64&\bord2\3c&H6411EB&\fad(0,200)}Everyone has their own little cosmos which we call "heart."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.41,0:01:59.23,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAubrey\fs50\c&HFFFFFF&\frz1.12\be1\blur4\3a&H64&\bord2\3c&H1BFFFA&\fad(0,200)}It's tightly packed with emotions and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:02.98,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAubrey\fs50\c&HFFFFFF&\frz1.12\be1\blur4\3a&H64&\bord2\3c&HA0756F&\fad(0,200)}We're busy getting excited, blue, or in{\fnArial}-{\fn}between.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:06.34,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAubrey\fs50\c&HFFFFFF&\frz1.12\be1\blur4\3a&H64&\bord2\3c&HF56CF1&}It's chaos every day, so might as well make a song out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.34,0:02:07.67,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAubrey\fs50\c&HFFFFFF&\frz1.12\be1\blur4\3a&H64&\bord2\3c&HF56CF1&}And sing all about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:11.98,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAubrey\fs50\c&HFFFFFF&\frz1.12\be1\blur4\3a&H64&\bord2\3c&HA2C26B&\fad(0,200)}We unconsciously study music even in class.
